data.text:
Dwayne Carter is a character role-played by AfricanSnowball.

General Description[]

Dwayne Carter is a Sergeant for the Los Santos Police Department, Badge #450.

He was previously a Corrections Officer for the Department of Corrections, Badge #733.

Personality[]

Carter goes hard in the paint, and always he wants someone to have a good ass day.

[]
